  "detailed_description": "<h1>About Us</h1><p>We are F-Greetings Studio from Chengdu. As a college student, I am clear that due to my limited experience there might be some mistakes and flows. And I develop this game by myself. As producer of this game, I accept criticism. I would appreciate it if you can give me some advice. You can contact me.</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/942010/extras/4fa769dfa213a91ff68cf0562b447fda.poster.avif?t=1726045137\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/942010/extras/4fa769dfa213a91ff68cf0562b447fda.webm?t=1726045137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/942010/extras/4fa769dfa213a91ff68cf0562b447fda.mp4?t=1726045137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>“Remember it? Remember it! ” I can’t remember anything. Somebody keeps speaking to me: ”Where are you? Where are you? ” I need to go into my mind and find myself! I have come to this place named “The Third Building”. My memory is buried here. “The Third Building” is a first-person horror game. Play this “cursed” game to find the secrets about me and an indie-game studio in the third building.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/942010/extras/8fb08ddbed82b46d8eea4bfb9f797c54.poster.avif?t=1726045137\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/942010/extras/8fb08ddbed82b46d8eea4bfb9f797c54.webm?t=1726045137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/942010/extras/8fb08ddbed82b46d8eea4bfb9f797c54.mp4?t=1726045137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Every college has a haunted building</h2>This game is based on true stories from the producer. I hope I can tell my story. But after all game is not reality. The scariest thing is reality. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/942010/extras/d57e6d280e1974253dd05d0cdc028497.poster.avif?t=1726045137\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/942010/extras/d57e6d280e1974253dd05d0cdc028497.webm?t=1726045137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/942010/extras/d57e6d280e1974253dd05d0cdc028497.mp4?t=1726045137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/942010/extras/4fa769dfa213a91ff68cf0562b447fda.poster.avif?t=1726045137\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/942010/extras/4fa769dfa213a91ff68cf0562b447fda.webm?t=1726045137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/942010/extras/4fa769dfa213a91ff68cf0562b447fda.mp4?t=1726045137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>“Remember it? Remember it! ” I can’t remember anything. Somebody keeps speaking to me: ”Where are you? Where are you? ” I need to go into my mind and find myself! I have come to this place named “The Third Building”. My memory is buried here. “The Third Building” is a first-person horror game. Play this “cursed” game to find the secrets about me and an indie-game studio in the third building.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/942010/extras/8fb08ddbed82b46d8eea4bfb9f797c54.poster.avif?t=1726045137\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/942010/extras/8fb08ddbed82b46d8eea4bfb9f797c54.webm?t=1726045137\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/942010/extras/8fb08ddbed82b46d8eea4bfb9f797c54.mp4?t=1726045137\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Every college has a haunted building</h2>This game is based on true stories from the producer. I hope I can tell my story. But after all game is not reality. The scariest thing is reality. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai